265
00:13:46,082 --> 00:13:51,038
When I tell you to start a central line, you
start a central line - no judgment, no question.

266
00:13:51,135 --> 00:13:53,846
Guy's been in seven hospitals in the
last four months. He's a major addict.

267
00:13:53,947 --> 00:13:56,286
The patient has a three-lumbar fusion.

268
00:13:56,368 --> 00:13:58,246
He's a junkie. We shouldn't be giving him -

269
00:13:58,308 --> 00:14:01,299
Yeah, he's an addict, but his pain is real.

270
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:04,262
Lose the attitude, get down
there, start a central line.

271
00:14:21,245 --> 00:14:24,963
Told me I had a towel inside me.

272
00:14:25,506 --> 00:14:26,561
Who told you that?

273
00:14:27,856 --> 00:14:30,924
A surgeon - an older man.

274
00:14:31,476 --> 00:14:32,576
Handsome.

275
00:14:33,176 --> 00:14:34,435
That's Dr. Webber.

276
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:35,654
He's our chief.

277
00:14:36,152 --> 00:14:36,918
Yeah.

278
00:14:38,348 --> 00:14:44,568
It was a towel that somebody left the last time.

279
00:14:44,675 --> 00:14:45,527
Yes, ma'am.

280
00:14:45,987 --> 00:14:47,441
Who would do that?

281
00:14:50,682 --> 00:14:52,867
That doesn't seem right, does it?

282
00:14:56,544 --> 00:14:57,998
No, ma'am, no.

283
00:14:58,534 --> 00:14:59,421
It doesn't.

284
00:15:00,834 --> 00:15:04,311
I was walking around with a towel inside of me.

285
00:15:04,987 --> 00:15:06,855
How could that happen?

286
00:15:46,614 --> 00:15:49,223
So? What happens now?

287
00:15:54,692 --> 00:15:57,549
Now you keep this to yourself
while we work it out.

288
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,134
Do this for me.

289
00:16:17,477 --> 00:16:18,189
You okay?

290
00:16:18,424 --> 00:16:19,540
Yeah, yeah, I'm good.

291
00:16:19,622 --> 00:16:21,036
Are you sure? Because you seem not okay.

292
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:24,193
I'm fine. Cabg was long.

293
00:16:24,291 --> 00:16:27,093
Well, let me take you out to dinner tonight.
You can tell me all about it.

294
00:16:27,231 --> 00:16:30,189
Real food, waiters, big
chunks of carbs in a basket.

295
00:16:30,425 --> 00:16:31,137
I can't.

296
00:16:31,531 --> 00:16:32,376
Forget the party.

297
00:16:32,801 --> 00:16:33,893
You know about the party?

298
00:16:33,994 --> 00:16:36,748
Your friends will be at the party. You
and I can be alone somewhere else.

299
00:16:36,911 --> 00:16:38,151
How do you know about the party?

300
00:16:38,242 --> 00:16:40,665
Thanks for not inviting me, by the way.
That felt good.

301
00:16:40,869 --> 00:16:42,974
Dinner - think about dinner. Perfect opportunity.

302
00:16:43,322 --> 00:16:43,998
Well...

303
00:16:48,684 --> 00:16:49,339
What happened?

304
00:16:49,472 --> 00:16:52,354
Started having swelling over her
sternum, then blood started gushing.

305
00:16:52,411 --> 00:16:53,706
Dr. Burke is on his way right now.

306
00:16:53,798 --> 00:16:54,780
Is she dying?

307
00:16:54,981 --> 00:16:57,483
Somebody get him out of here.
Keep applying pressure.

308
00:16:57,967 --> 00:16:59,771
Tyler, call for an O.R.

309
00:16:59,855 --> 00:17:01,371
What the hell happened? She got her protamine?

310
00:17:01,479 --> 00:17:05,104
Per protocol. No allergic,
anaphylactic, or histamine responses.

311
00:17:05,985 --> 00:17:07,126
Her last counts?

312
00:17:07,525 --> 00:17:11,329
B.T., P.T.T., I.N.R., platelet
