322
00:17:42,984 --> 00:17:44,054
- Suction...
- Suction...

323
00:17:44,255 --> 00:17:44,910
I'm sorry.

324
00:17:44,977 --> 00:17:46,934
And then you confess in front of her husband?

325
00:17:47,944 --> 00:17:50,573
