326
00:17:50,675 --> 00:17:51,673
I'm sorry.

327
00:17:58,371 --> 00:17:59,133
Over here.

328
00:18:00,255 --> 00:18:01,002
There.

329
00:18:01,633 --> 00:18:03,135
Look at the wall rupture.

330
00:18:03,301 --> 00:18:05,242
It's a hell of a lot more than a fingernail.

331
00:18:05,677 --> 00:18:07,725
Her ventricular walls are weak.

332
00:18:09,016 --> 00:18:12,261
I just had a conversation with Mr. Patterson.

333
00:18:12,436 --> 00:18:16,065
I want copies of his wife's
chart in my office by 5:00.

334
00:18:16,139 --> 00:18:18,691
Tomorrow, the two of you are
going to meet with me and legal,

335
00:18:18,731 --> 00:18:21,682
and you better damn well be able
to explain what happened here.

336
00:18:23,638 --> 00:18:26,526
People poking holes in hearts and leaving towels.

337
00:18:27,317 --> 00:18:30,596
You're gonna go back and talk to the husband.

338
00:18:30,806 --> 00:18:32,153
Review the history.

339
00:18:32,287 --> 00:18:34,805
Apologize profusely.

340
00:18:35,358 --> 00:18:37,447
Your ass is on the line here, Dr. Grey.

341
00:18:42,275 --> 00:18:43,745
You got called before the chief?

342
00:18:43,811 --> 00:18:44,979
Tomorrow morning.

343
00:18:45,106 --> 00:18:46,888
I could get kicked out of the program.

344
00:18:47,763 --> 00:18:48,956
