345
00:18:49,043 --> 00:18:50,037
You're not getting kicked out.

346
00:18:50,133 --> 00:18:51,409
Patterson's just gonna sue.

347
00:18:51,517 --> 00:18:52,986
Patterson is not going to sue.

348
00:18:53,068 --> 00:18:54,425
You're not getting kicked out.

349
00:18:54,512 --> 00:18:57,184
