379
00:20:21,329 --> 00:20:23,386
And how do we make it stop?

380
00:20:39,427 --> 00:20:40,252
Dr. Yang.

381
00:20:41,347 --> 00:20:42,156
Dr. Burke.

382
00:20:45,341 --> 00:20:47,461
That bypass graft got a little complicated.

383
00:20:48,199 --> 00:20:49,796
It's nothing I couldn't handle.

384
00:20:51,177 --> 00:20:51,741
Good.

385
00:21:01,933 --> 00:21:02,693
Yeah.

386
00:21:07,401 --> 00:21:10,168
Listen, I'll call you back.

387
00:21:13,547 --> 00:21:16,296
That was my lawyer. He's
advising me not to talk to you.

388
00:21:16,383 --> 00:21:19,870
Mr. Patterson, I know that
you're frustrated and angry,

389
00:21:19,952 --> 00:21:24,673
