396
00:21:36,178 --> 00:21:37,520
She had lost 100 pounds.

397
00:21:37,587 --> 00:21:39,695
Don't you dare try to hang this on her.

398
00:21:40,047 --> 00:21:42,342
- Mr. Patterson, please.
- We're through talking.

399
00:22:05,545 --> 00:22:08,014
