400
00:22:08,252 --> 00:22:13,390
Oh, Jerry, it's not you specifically.
It's just people like you, that's all.

401
00:22:14,153 --> 00:22:16,620
Doc, I'm feeling pretty good.

402
00:22:16,835 --> 00:22:18,909
Pain's about a 3.

403
00:22:18,971 --> 00:22:20,768
A 3? That's excellent.

404
00:22:21,115 --> 00:22:25,615
Mr. Frost, I'm glad we could help you out,
as well as county, mercy west, seattle pres.

405
00:22:25,678 --> 00:22:27,853
A lot of people have helped you out lately, Jerry.

406
00:22:27,895 --> 00:22:29,150
We're pleased we could do our part.

407
00:22:29,436 --> 00:22:31,223
Who's on discharge today, Dr. Karev?

408
00:22:31,351 --> 00:22:32,410
Izzie Stevens.

409
00:22:32,594 --> 00:22:34,790
Mr. Frost, Dr. Stevens is gonna discharge you.

410
00:22:34,863 --> 00:22:36,548
Whoa, you can't discharge me.

411
00:22:36,619 --> 00:22:38,923
- I'm in pain.
- You were in pain. Now you're not.

412
00:22:39,189 --> 00:22:43,111
Dr. Karev here is going to recommend some
wonderful treatment programs for you.

413
00:22:43,183 --> 00:22:43,966
Go home.

414
00:22:44,365 --> 00:22:45,416
Get some help.

415
00:22:45,712 --> 00:22:47,059
You can't just do that!

416
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:48,527
He just did, my friend.

417
00:22:50,869 --> 00:22:52,823
Okay, any luck yet?

418
00:22:53,284 --> 00:22:54,283
Nada.

419
00:22:55,076 --> 00:22:57,442
Ugh. Looks like you're gonna
have to spend another night.

420
00:22:58,097 --> 00:22:59,971
I hate to miss the party.

421
00:23:00,519 --> 00:23:01,660
You gonna make it?

422
00:23:01,797 --> 00:23:05,066
You are the last person on my list,
so it's looking pretty good.

423
00:23:05,152 --> 00:23:08,599
So, doctors have lives after all.
Who'd have thunk?

424
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:11,773
