425
00:23:15,168 --> 00:23:16,520
Don't look at me like that.

426
00:23:16,678 --> 00:23:17,988
It's not gonna take very long.

427
00:23:19,499 --> 00:23:20,221
It's not.

428
00:23:25,926 --> 00:23:26,770
You paged me?

429
00:23:26,964 --> 00:23:29,566
I'm gonna be a while. Do you think you
could get home to sign for the beer?

430
00:23:29,657 --> 00:23:32,125
Why don't you have your boyfriend sign for it?

431
00:23:33,744 --> 00:23:36,729
You have a very annoying way
of sneaking up on people.

432
00:23:36,939 --> 00:23:38,648
Maybe if you were a little less creepy...

433
00:23:38,741 --> 00:23:39,915
I wouldn't come anyway.

434
00:23:40,077 --> 00:23:41,169
I hate big parties.

435
00:23:41,307 --> 00:23:44,416
Is Meredith the only person who
doesn't know the size of this thing?

436
00:23:44,507 --> 00:23:45,565
I'm telling her.

437
00:23:45,746 --> 00:23:47,108
You can't. She's gone already.

438
00:23:47,189 --> 00:23:48,091
What, already?

439
00:23:48,311 --> 00:23:52,391
I think she had - um, excuse
me - an errand to run.

440
00:23:53,303 --> 00:23:55,950
You don't think Meredith's going to mind, right?

441
00:23:56,028 --> 00:23:59,785
