442
00:23:59,861 --> 00:24:00,723
nothing.

443
00:24:12,754 --> 00:24:14,516
Oh, I'm sorry I'm late. It was the traffic.

444
00:24:14,576 --> 00:24:15,636
It doesn't matter, dear.

445
00:24:15,763 --> 00:24:17,900
Okay. Don't tell me the notary didn't show.

446
00:24:17,961 --> 00:24:20,751
Oh, everybody's here. It's just your mother isn't.

447
00:24:23,122 --> 00:24:23,864
Mom?

448
00:24:24,484 --> 00:24:25,113
Mom?

449
00:24:25,768 --> 00:24:26,972
What do you people want from me?

450
00:24:27,396 --> 00:24:29,389
We need you to sign the lawyer's papers.

451
00:24:29,466 --> 00:24:32,318
I have a cranial reconstruction
in a half an hour. I need to go.

452
00:24:32,404 --> 00:24:34,201
Okay, mom. We're all here.

453
00:24:34,273 --> 00:24:35,268
We have a notary.

454
00:24:35,436 --> 00:24:36,747
I need you to focus,

455
00:24:36,961 --> 00:24:38,929
and I need you to sign these papers.

456
00:24:40,560 --> 00:24:42,891
Mom, look at me.

457
00:24:44,283 --> 00:24:45,850
It's an emergency surgery.

458
00:24:45,942 --> 00:24:46,981
I don't have time for this.

459
00:24:47,084 --> 00:24:48,722
She can't sign anything now.

460
00:24:48,896 --> 00:24:51,353
We should have done this earlier in the day.

461
00:24:51,415 --> 00:24:53,177
I couldn't come earlier in the day.

462
00:24:53,279 --> 00:24:56,510
I have a job and a life, and I'm here now.

463
00:24:56,597 --> 00:24:59,336
You're gonna have to come back
tomorrow, when she's lucid.

464
00:24:59,476 --> 00:25:02,097
You know, why did she put this off for so long?

465
00:25:02,183 --> 00:25:03,550
And why did you let her?

466
00:25:03,616 --> 00:25:06,120
Doesn't it strike you as slightly irresponsible?

467
00:25:06,219 --> 00:25:08,620
I mean, what the hell is wrong with you people?!

468
00:26:31,404 --> 00:26:33,821
Izzie, I'm gonna kill you.

469
00:26:40,827 --> 00:26:43,311
