483
00:27:22,836 --> 00:27:24,825
Just give me the hit of demerol.

484
00:27:25,387 --> 00:27:26,898
The dilaudid hasn't worn off yet.

485
00:27:26,955 --> 00:27:29,803
- Mr. Frost, you have to...
- Look, I'm not leaving.

486
00:27:29,904 --> 00:27:30,830
I'm calling psych.

487
00:27:30,922 --> 00:27:33,099
No, no. Don't call psych.

488
00:27:33,180 --> 00:27:33,964
Wait, wait, wait.

489
00:27:34,445 --> 00:27:36,422
Stop, Jerry. Stop. Stop. Stop.

490
00:27:41,268 --> 00:27:42,950
Jerry. Jerry!

