508
00:28:53,069 --> 00:28:54,624
I told her to clear it with you.

509
00:28:54,748 --> 00:28:56,657
I can't handle this.

510
00:28:56,776 --> 00:28:58,388
You want me to kick everyone out?

511
00:28:58,865 --> 00:29:00,764
I'm gonna kick everyone out.

512
00:29:03,886 --> 00:29:06,402
Baby, you made it! Whoo!

