582
00:32:51,437 --> 00:32:53,096
I work 100-hour weeks.

583
00:32:53,486 --> 00:32:55,661
I can't always show up to my own parties on time.

584
00:32:55,743 --> 00:32:57,873
My patients have to come first. It's just...

585
00:32:58,078 --> 00:33:03,010
Yeah, I just flew across the entire country,
and there's a hundred people at your house.

586
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:05,062
A hundred people who understand what I do all day.

587
00:33:05,450 --> 00:33:07,196
I shouldn't have to apologize for that.

588
00:33:07,714 --> 00:33:09,199
No, you shouldn't.

589
00:33:16,674 --> 00:33:19,874
Look, let's just go by the
party for a little while.

590
00:33:20,305 --> 00:33:22,910
You'll really like everyone once
you get a chance to know them.

591
00:33:25,047 --> 00:33:26,105
I should just go.

592
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:27,754
Hank, come on.

593
00:33:30,837 --> 00:33:31,695
I'll call you.

594
00:34:28,659 --> 00:34:30,864
You know, in some states,
you get arrested for that.

595
00:34:44,403 --> 00:34:46,587
So, you blew me off for a bottle of tequila.

596
00:34:46,910 --> 00:34:48,169
Tequila's no good for you -

597
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:49,722
doesn't call, doesn't write.

598
00:34:49,937 --> 00:34:52,067
It's not nearly as much fun to wake up to.

599
00:35:06,551 --> 00:35:08,318
Take me for a ride, Derek.

600
00:35:14,205 --> 00:35:16,607
You know, it sounds like the party's winding down.

601
00:35:17,118 --> 00:35:18,987
- Listen to me!
- What?

602
00:35:19,065 --> 00:35:20,862
We should probably sneak inside now.

603
00:35:21,932 --> 00:35:24,036
We've done enough sneaking for the night.

604
00:35:24,103 --> 00:35:25,956
It was good sneaking, but enough sneaking.

605
00:35:26,023 --> 00:35:27,492
Yeah, I'd say we're pretty good sneakers.

606
00:35:33,594 --> 00:35:35,509
You mind moving this tail wagon?

607
00:35:35,581 --> 00:35:36,933
You're blocking me in.

608
00:35:40,208 --> 00:35:41,629
Apparently not good enough.

609
00:36:11,163 --> 00:36:12,697
When's your meeting with the chief?

610
00:36:14,809 --> 00:36:15,935
In an hour.

611
00:36:21,018 --> 00:36:23,041
Holy mother of destruction.

612
00:36:23,420 --> 00:36:25,371
You missed doctor-palooza.

613
00:36:26,690 --> 00:36:28,320
Apparently, you didn't.

614
00:36:28,976 --> 00:36:31,268
I should probably never speak to you again.

615
00:36:32,555 --> 00:36:33,926
I'm so sorry, Meredith.

616
00:36:34,315 --> 00:36:36,169
I had no idea it was going to get so...

617
00:36:36,989 --> 00:36:37,852
It's okay.

618
00:36:38,528 --> 00:36:40,008
Really, I don't care.

619
00:36:40,945 --> 00:36:42,619
What would I be doing, anyway?

620
00:36:42,871 --> 00:36:45,046
Preparing for your career-altering meeting.

621
00:36:45,221 --> 00:36:46,173
Sorry.

622
00:36:46,331 --> 00:36:48,210
That heart wall shouldn't have torn.

623
00:36:48,912 --> 00:36:50,525
Anything in the patient's history?

624
00:36:51,513 --> 00:36:54,400
Husband said she was in the
best shape of her life.

625
00:36:54,759 --> 00:36:57,084
She lost 100 pounds last year.

626
00:36:57,867 --> 00:37:00,442
100 pounds in a year - how's her muscle mass?

627
00:37:04,334 --> 00:37:06,279
Do you even know whose that was?

628
00:37:07,317 --> 00:37:08,460
I'm hoping it was yours.

629
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:09,576
No.

630
00:37:13,261 --> 00:37:14,688
What do you think?

631
00:37:15,727 --> 00:37:20,091
50 says Meredith gets tossed out on
her ass and Burke walks away clean.

632
00:37:20,183 --> 00:37:21,396
Please be nice to her.

633
00:37:23,045 --> 00:37:25,953
So, I have done a lot of research on this,

634
00:37:26,004 --> 00:37:28,257
and Dr. Burke has been kind enough to help me.

635
00:37:28,319 --> 00:37:32,528
And I understand my responsibility
in what I've done wrong here.

636
00:37:32,594 --> 00:37:37,155
However, I do think the patient's
history is significant in this case.

637
00:37:37,227 --> 00:37:39,270
She still weighs 200 pounds,

638
00:37:39,341 --> 00:37:41,282
which is why no one even noticed it.

639
00:37:41,369 --> 00:37:44,395
