was losing heart muscle.

642
00:37:49,408 --> 00:37:52,644
That certainly could be the reason for
a small poke to become a large tear.

643
00:37:52,701 --> 00:37:54,578
That still doesn't change the fact, though.

644
00:37:54,620 --> 00:37:57,697
The small poke wasn't reported at
the time of the occurrence.

645
00:37:57,733 --> 00:38:00,529
- And if I could change that...
- And you can't.

646
00:38:00,621 --> 00:38:03,871
You've left yourself and the hospital
open to a tremendous amount of liability.

647
00:38:03,929 --> 00:38:07,259
- Not if the weight loss caused the problem.
- I'm sorry, I've no choice...

648
00:38:07,315 --> 00:38:11,879
I've spoken to the husband, and I believe
as long as his wife remains stable -

649
00:38:11,948 --> 00:38:15,310
