650
00:38:15,424 --> 00:38:17,778
- Dr. Grey made a huge error here.
- And she reported it.

651
00:38:17,844 --> 00:38:18,684
Too late.

652
00:38:18,756 --> 00:38:20,599
And in front of the patient's husband.

653
00:38:20,686 --> 00:38:22,576
But she reported it. She spoke up.

654
00:38:26,462 --> 00:38:28,514
Five years ago, as a C.T. fellow,

655
00:38:28,782 --> 00:38:31,295
I had a nagging feeling that I
didn't check the body cavity

656
00:38:31,330 --> 00:38:34,050
