fear of liability could end my career.

662
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:58,927
Even great doctors make mistakes, and when we do,

663
00:38:59,005 --> 00:39:02,742
we've got to have a chance to speak
up without fear of retribution.

664
00:39:03,434 --> 00:39:04,832
